title: BoostBird Singing in the Trend of Zeit 5/19: Rihanna, Dark MAGA, Migos, Monkeypox, McDonalds, Defense Production Act, Attack of the Clones
itunes:title: BoostBird Singing in the Trend of Zeit 5/19: Rihanna, Dark MAGA, Migos, Monkeypox, McDonalds, Defense Production Act, Attack of the Clones
description:
In this edition of BoostBird Singing in the Trend of Zeit, Jack and special guest co-host Matt Lieb discuss Rihanna welcoming her first baby with A$AP Rocky, Madison Cawthorn proclaiming it's time for 'Dark MAGA' to take command, Migos possibly breaking up, Monkeypox cases detected in Europe & North America, McDonald's selling off all of their Russian locations, Biden invoking the Defense Production Act for the baby formula shortage, and and Ewan McGregor's "Attack of the Clones" revelation.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
